author: Carly Ledbetter
title: Kendall Jenner Steps Out In London Wearing 2 Gold Teeth
text:
Kendall Jenner Steps Out In London Wearing 2 Gold Teeth 😐 😐 😐 By Carly Ledbetter 
Kendall Jenner stepped out wearing an interesting look in London on Monday night. 
The 21-year-old model, who is in town for London Fashion Week, wore an oversize knit sweater over a cream dress, paired with black boots and bright red lips. But the most contentious part of her outfit was the two gold teeth she added to her look: WeirPhotos / Splash News A post shared by Bella Hadid (@bellahadid) on Feb 20, 2017 at 4:51pm PST Ricky Vigil via Getty Images Kendall Jenner arriving at Cirque le Soir club after attending the Love Me 17 X Burberry party on Feb. 20. 
Jenner donned gold teeth, and her sisters (specifically Kylie, Kim and Khloe) have a history of wearing grills , whether it’s for magazine covers , birthday celebrations or just an Instagram photo or two. 💎💎💎 A photo posted by Kim Kardashian West (@kimkardashian) on Sep 29, 2016 at 12:40pm PDT A post shared by Kendall (@kendalljenner) on Jun 26, 2014 at 7:53pm PDT A post shared by Kylie (@kyliejenner) on Sep 3, 2013 at 9:40pm PDT
